thread.title: Comments competition: Entries closed

author: news24.com
title: Comments competition: Entries closed
text:
ENTRIES for our MyNews24 competition on comments are now closed.
We will consider all articles submitted prior to 08:00 this morning, even if they have not been published yet today.
The two winners will be announced on Tuesday at 14:00, on MyNews24 as well as on New24's social media accounts.
Thank you for all the submissions.
